overview: Rama, Garin, Farel, Quincy and Celsi survive from the spirit terror at the Ayunan Island resort which harbored a terrible history of the slaughter of a family and resort employees. Rama is frantic: her lover is in a mental hospital, the body of Hana, his sister, and Fira have not been found. Rama returns to Ayunan Island to look for them. But obstacles lay ahead.
title: Kembalinya Anak Iblis
